  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nWhen messages are received close together and pinned then the username corresponding to the second message is not shown. This may be confusing when determining who has sent each message.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Send multiple messages close together from different users\r\n2. Pin the messages\r\n3. View pinned messages\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nUsers can easily determine who has sent each pinned message.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50769329/186414600-3df56658-e62e-49ab-8357-d68d3b0dff59.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: https://ci.status.im/job/status-desktop/job/platforms/job/macos/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/pkg/StatusIm-Desktop-220824-111243-1c7719.dmg\r\n- Operating System: Mac\r\n\r\n",
